                    "body": "Reclassifying as minor new feature.  The use case you describe is not in the scope of the current Zend_Form_Element_File \/ Zend_View_Helper_FormFile pair.  What you will need to do is extend the existing elements to create a \"combo element\" class.  An example of how this is done can be seen here (it's a three-field date element, but the principle is the same)\r\nhttp:\/\/akrabat.com\/zend-framework\/a-zend-framwork-compount-form-element-for-dates\/",
